    <div class="advisor-copy">
      Cash is ${fmt(cash)} with a ${fmt(reserveFloor)} floor. Priority bills funded from the current plan: ${fmt(funded)}. ${nextUnfunded ? `Next unfunded bill: ${esc(nextUnfunded.bill.name)} for ${fmt(nextUnfunded.amountDue)}.` : 'No urgent unfunded bill is currently showing.'}
